Mishti Chakravarty is an Indian Actress. Mishti Chakravarty’s birthday is on 20th December in the year of 1987. As of 2022, Mishti Chakravarty is 35 years of age. Mishti Chakravarty ’s Zodiac sign is Saggitarius. Mishti Chakravarty was born in Kolkata.

Mishti Chakravarty went to a local school in Kolkata. Mishti Chakravarty also graduated from Kolkata University in English Literature.

Mishti Chakravarty made her Bollywood debut in Subhash Ghai's Kaanchi: The Unbreakable and her Telugu debut in Nithiin-A. Karunakaran's Chinnadana Nee Kosam and with Prithviraj Sukumaran and Jinu Abraham's Adam Joan, Mishti Chakravarty made her Malayalam film debut.

Columbus, Mishti Chakravarty's upcoming Telugu film, starring Sumanth Ashwin and is produced by MS Raju.

With Indra Kumar's Great Grand Masti, the third instalment in the Masti film series, Mishti Chakravarty returned to Bollywood. Mishti Chakravarty starred alongside Naseeruddin Shah and Vidya Balan in Srijit Mukherji's historical film Begum Jaan in 2017. Mishti Chakravarty played Shabnam in the film, which was set against the backdrop of a brothel. At the Indian box office, the picture did a mediocre job.

Indrani Chakraborty, professionally known as Mishti, is an Indian actress who works primarily in Telugu and Hindi films. Mishti Chakravarty has appeared in a number of films, including Kaanchi: The Unbreakable (2014), Chinnadana Nee Kosam (2014), Adam Joan (2017), Brihaspathi (2018), and Burra Katha (2019). Mishti Chakravarty was recently seen in music videos like Zahin Kare and Hath Fadle by Zee Music.

Mishti Chakravarty is single.
